text:
Sorry, I might have made
the menu a bit too tough from the start.

Tenka wants to push through...to the end...
and level up...

If you have that determination, it'll be fine.
Let's get through this together to the end!

If we clear it...
there'll be an amazing reward...!
Haha, it's like a game, huh?

──But as a reward after lessons,
it might be nice to prepare something.
Like preparing something a bit extravagant.

An extravagant reward...!
Producer-san, will you prepare it...?

Hehe...
What should... the reward... be...!
